	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Perfect for learning SMT soldering? Sure.
<br />
<br />But I wouldn't personally use a purely microcontroller-based 'scope, logic analyzer, or function generator though; the bandwidth micros can support just isn't high enough.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


