	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Over the past year I've been building various boards that tie into the NES.  I picked up an old Hitachi 20MHz analog scope and it's by far the most useful tool in my collection.  I'd love to pick up a logic analyzer like the one you referenced, but I can honestly say I wouldn't have been able to get to the point I'm at without an analog scope.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
